Description: Women with rich style will want to travel with this oversized Guess® shopper tote; complete with a repeating Guess G pattern against a luxurious black-sheened background. Interior is fully lined with a bold triangle print. Two additional large zippered main compartments feature additional pockets for your smartphone and other belongings. Five metal bottom feet. Rear trolley pass-through. 10" handle drop height with vinyl snap wrap. Includes Guess vinyl identification tag for decorating. Signature Guess hardware and branding. Size: 13.75" H X 7" W X 18" L
